Package: quantrecipes
Title: Extra recipes for quantitative analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
  person(
    given = "R. Dimas Bagas",
    family = "Herlambang",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "bagasbgy@gmail.com"
  )
Description: A set of data preprocess recipes for quantitative analysis.
  This package shipped some custom steps to produces several quantitative
  analysis information, such as Bollinger Bands, Moving Averages, etc.
URL: https://github.com/bagasbgy/quantrecipes
BugReports: https://github.com/bagasbgy/quantrecipes/issues
